title: Worklight

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a worklight, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a front perspective view of a worklight;
FIG. 2 is a rear perspective view thereof;
FIG. 3 is a front elevation view thereof;
FIG. 4 is a right side elevation view thereof;
FIG. 5 is a rear elevation view thereof;
FIG. 6 is a left elevation view thereof;
FIG. 7 is a top plan view thereof; and,
FIG. 8 is a bottom plan view thereof.
The broken lines which define the bounds the claimed design form no part of the claimed design.
